<h2 id="290">3. Personalising plentymarkets POS</h2>
<div class="sectionbody">
<div class="sect2">
<h3 id="_customising_the_screen">3.1. Customising the screen</h3>
<div class="paragraph instruction">
<p>Customising the screen:</p>
</div>
<div class="olist arabic">
<ol class="arabic">
<li>
<p>Go to <strong>Settings » Item » Attributes</strong>.</p>
</li>
<li>
<p>Click on the attribute.</p>
</li>
<li>
<p>Open the <strong>Values</strong> tab.</p>
</li>
<li>
<p>Click on <strong>New value</strong>.</p>
</li>
<li>
<p>Enter the internal name.</p>
</li>
<li>
<p><strong>Save</strong> the settings.<br>
→ The attribute value is assigned an ID and displayed in the <strong>Values</strong> tab.</p>
</li>
<li>
<p>Carry out additional settings as desired. Pay attention to the information given in table 2.</p>
</li>
<li>
