</tr>
</thead>
<tbody>
<tr>
<td class="tableblock halign-left valign-top"><p class="tableblock"><strong>Not paid</strong></p></td>
<td class="tableblock halign-left valign-top"><p class="tableblock">Customer does not receive any money.<br>
A credit note for the returned items is created in the background.<br>
<strong><em>Tipp:</em></strong> The invoice amount the customer still needs to pay is shown on the credit note receipt.</p></td>
