<p>Returned items cost more than the unpaid invoice amount = The customer receives the balance of the unpaid invoice amount minus the price of the returned items. <br></p>
</li>
</ul>
</div>
<div class="paragraph">
<p>A credit note for the returned items is created in the background. Note that the credit note amount and the refunded amount are not always the same. If the refunded amount does not match the credit note amount, the refunded amount is shown on the credit note receipt.</p>
